## How to defer LoyaltyLion on /cart

The codebase already uses the document.createElement override pattern for
Reamaze (meu epic, commit cc8d92d) and BookThatApp (ed3d161). Apply the
same pattern scoped to /cart only.

### Step 1 — Audit how LoyaltyLion loads

Check layout/theme.liquid and the ly-global snippet (app embed) for how
sdk.loyaltylion.net is injected. It is likely via content_for_header
(Shopify app embed), which means the createElement override is the correct
